    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem">The Capoccia and Miotto families share Italian heritage. Their reunion tradition began in <strong>1977</strong> and continues as a gift to every generation.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">The Capoccia and Miotto branches were joined when <strong>Anna M. Capoccia</strong> married <strong>Amerigo “Mickey” Miotto</strong>, creating the family bond this website proudly honors. Anna’s brothers, <strong>George Capoccia</strong> and <strong>Tony Capoccia</strong>, remain central to that living connection.</p>

